Get Teamstaffel Results Table

Source: R/teamstaffel.R
get_results.Rd

Get Teamstaffel Results Table

Usage

get_results(
  sex = "M",
  year = 2022,
  event = "ALL",
  base_url = "https://berlin-wasserbetriebe.r.mikatiming.de"
)

Arguments

sex

either "M" for men or "W" for women default: "M"

year

default: 2022

event

return overall results ("ALL") or of a selected starting day (i.e. "ST1", "ST2" or "ST3"), (default: "ALL")

base_url

default: "https://berlin-wasserbetriebe.r.mikatiming.de"

Value

tibble with results

Examples

women <- get_results("W")
women
